 File the PR against the correct branch: master, 4.3.x, 5.0.x. Default: master.
 Copy the technical committee to review the pull request if your PR is targeting a particular programming language: @jebentier (2017/07), @dkarlovi (2017/07), @mandrean (2017/08), @jfastnacht (2017/09), @ackintosh (2017/09) heart, @ybelenko (2018/07), @renepardon (2018/12), @wing328

I'm including a yaml file with an excerpt from the Webshipper API definition, which I'm using successfully after adding these changes to my own fork of openapi-generator.
